data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the prestigious community of Portico! This stunning single-family home offers the perfect blend of luxury and comfort, with all the features you've been searching for. Boasting 4 spacious bedrooms and 2 beautifully appointed bathrooms, this home provides ample space for your family to grow and thrive. The 3-car garage ensures plenty of room for all your vehicles and storage needs. Step outside and be greeted by your very own oasis - an in-ground pool with a spa, perfect for relaxing and entertaining. Enjoy the breathtaking lake view as you soak up the Florida sunshine in your private backyard.  Inside, you'll find a well-designed office space, ideal for those who work from home or need a quiet area for studying. The kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring granite counters and stainless steel appliances that will inspire your culinary creations. The carpet and tile flooring throughout the home add a touch of elegance and comfort. No detail has been overlooked in this home, with upgraded lighting and fans that enhance the ambiance and style.  While the screened-in front entry provides an extra layer of security and privacy. With gutters in place, you can rest easy knowing that your home is protected from the elements. This home truly has it all - from the luxurious amenities to the stunning lake view, it's the perfect place to call home.
